{"tid":871354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"零食店男店長　幫上門女童Cos後襲胸遭逮","createTime":"2018-10-22T00:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T03:05:59.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c139947e9704e925f0faf395480778962fca1f5","tid":871354,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:59:26.000Z","msg":"日本茨城縣日立市的駄菓子店店長，因為對小學6年級女童襲胸，涉嫌猥褻遭逮，<br />\n <br />\n被逮後店長否認犯行。<br />\n <br />\n據《日視news24》報導，警方指出，44歲男子北浦亮，<br />\n <br />\n在今年8月於自己家中開設的駄菓子店中，<br />\n <br />\n對一名11歲小學6年級女童襲胸，涉嫌強制猥褻遭逮。<br />\n <br />\n而該間店鋪有放置各種Cosplay女僕裝，可以讓上門消費的孩童自由換裝，<br />\n <br />\n北浦亮則是在女童換裝後襲胸。警方表示，因為女童跟學校老師說，才讓這件事曝光。<br />\n <br />\n北浦亮的友人指出，「有聽過這件事(買女僕裝)，有聽說他喜歡萌系的角色」，<br />\n <br />\n對於警方的調查北浦亮全部否認，「我只碰到衣服，沒有碰到身體」。"},{"pid":"19dbedfea6a904453b4ce67d7f2972c9126122eb","tid":871354,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"我只係掂到港女塊平板無掂到個波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ad28a0da52b2360d4d82eb40cb8c4bf46d45f8","tid":871354,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"鬼國"},{"pid":"7ed635c808d5f51344de138be41aa3ace7321315","tid":871354,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3ad28a0da52b2360d4d82eb40cb8c4bf46d45f8","tid":871354,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"鬼國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:33:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾淫賤國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1370cdb4f0261221eed21b9b3dd50a696b22f7","tid":871354,"uid":73613,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:35:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"500d0c71b25a00d41bc19766e50e18eea23f714d","tid":871354,"uid":168342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c1370cdb4f0261221eed21b9b3dd50a696b22f7","tid":871354,"uid":73613,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"